<title>com.cyberway.issue.uid package</title>
</head>
<body>
A unique ID generator.
Default is {@link com.cyberway.issue.uid.UUIDGenerator}.  
To use another ID Generator, set the System Property
<code>com.cyberway.issue.uid.GeneratorFactory.generator</code> to point
at an alternate implementation of {@link com.cyberway.issue.uid.Generator}.

